column2: Purpose of listing TeliaSonera IC's Point of Presence in this Excel spreadsheet, is to provide our customers with an overview of possible interconnection points to TeliaSonera IC's network.
This list is subject to change without prior notice. TeliaSonera IC accepts no responsibility for errors or omissions. Always contact TeliaSonera IC for the latest updated information.
